quickml.supervised

Class PredictiveModelWithDataBuilder<R,PM extends PredictiveModel<R,?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • quickml.supervised.PredictiveModelWithDataBuilder<R,PM>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PredictiveModelBuilder<R,PM>, UpdatablePredictiveModelBuilder<R,PM>

    public class PredictiveModelWithDataBuilder<R,PM extends PredictiveModel<R,?>>
extends Object
implements UpdatablePredictiveModelBuilder<R,PM>
    PredictiveModelBuilder that supports adding data to predictive models The builder will keep track of the number of times the model has been built, and if the rebuild threshold is passed the model will be rebuilt If the split node threshold is passed the leaves will be rebuilt
